Sentencas: The compound Ba0.50Sr0.50Co0.80Fe0.20O3-delta (BSCF) has been used as a good candidate for air electrodes in Intermediate Temperature Solid Oxide Fuel Cells.
Titulo: Oxygen stoichiometry of Ba0.50Sr0.50Co0.80Fe0.20O3-δ obtained by EDTA-citrate method and measured by X-ray and neutron diffraction

Sentencas: Present work deals with the oxygen vacancy of this compound synthesized by using the EDTA-Citrate method.
Titulo: Oxygen stoichiometry of Ba0.50Sr0.50Co0.80Fe0.20O3-δ obtained by EDTA-citrate method and measured by X-ray and neutron diffraction

Sentencas: To obtain a single-phase sample, three portions of the compound were calcined at 700, 800 and 900 A degrees C. Only the sample calcined at 900 A degrees C showed a single phase.
Titulo: Oxygen stoichiometry of Ba0.50Sr0.50Co0.80Fe0.20O3-δ obtained by EDTA-citrate method and measured by X-ray and neutron diffraction

Sentencas: The stoichiometry of the single-phase sample, in particular of the oxygen atom, was determined by applying the combined X-ray and neutron Rietveld refinement to X-ray and neutron powder diffraction patterns measured with the sample.
Titulo: Oxygen stoichiometry of Ba0.50Sr0.50Co0.80Fe0.20O3-δ obtained by EDTA-citrate method and measured by X-ray and neutron diffraction
